| Type                                             | What Function Gets                        | Does original change? |
| ------------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------- | --------------------- |
| **Primitive (int, char, etc.)**                  | Copy of value                             | ❌ No                  |
| **Objects (Array, StringBuilder, custom class)** | Copy of reference (points to same object) | ✔ Yes                 |
in simple “Java is always pass-by-value, but for objects the value is a reference.”

video link :https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w4sGl3HxgZw